data.description: Enjoy the best of one-level living in this three bedroom, one full bath home. Enter inside where the living room welcomes you with a bright bay window. Luxury vinyl plank floors continue through to the dining area that has access to the rear yard, making indoor and outdoor living easy. Prepare your favorite meals in the kitchen that also includes laundry. Down the hall, the spacious primary bedroom is a luxurious retreat with a separate sitting area for lounging. Relax and unwind in the bathroom that boasts a walk-in glass-enclosed tile shower. Another two bedrooms complete this charming home. The fully-fenced rear yard has space for everyone’s activities and a storage shed. Tucked away at the end of a cul-de-sac with a fantastic location close to everything you need and major highways. Some images have been virtually staged.
